verse.lines:
{lang-eng}The company of angels are praising Thee on high,
And mortal men and all things created make reply.
The people of the Hebrews with psalms before Thee went;
Our praise and prayer and anthems before Thee We present.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}To Thee, before Thy passion, they sang their Hymns of praise;
To Thee, now high exalted, our melody we raise.
Thou didst accept their praises; accept the praise We bring,
Who in all good delightest, Thou good and gracious King.{/lang-eng}
